skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: valentine's gift ideas
des:
Struggling to think of a gift idea for valentines. Do they deserve something amazing and special - this skill may just help you out!

Simply say something like 'Alexa, start valentine's gift ideas'. Alexa will respond with a suitable suggestion for valentines.

And remember at the end of the day - the most important thing is you have each other :)
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
